			<content>
				<![CDATA[
				<h2>Overview</h2>
				<p>CARAMEL is a Content Managemant System for small sites and waived on an external database and an extensive user management. 
        Otherwise CARAMEL provides a lot of features to create a website according to your wishes. In addition, CARAMEL released under 
        the MIT license and may be used both for private and commercial purposes freely.
				</p>
				<h3>Features</h3>
				<ul>
				  <li>Easy to use interface</li>
				  <li>Support for multilingual websites</li>
				  <li>Integration of individual templates</li>
				</ul>
				]]>
			</content>
